description: My place is close to Central Park . You’ll love my place because of the light, the comfy bed, and the coziness. My place is good for couples, solo adventurers, and business travelers.
name: Beautiful cozzy apartment in the Upper East Side
review:
The apartment was very nice and clean and the location was very convenient. Emme also was very thorough making sure we had all of the information we needed to find her place and check in without any issues.
Thanks again!
